Package: rsurv
Type: Package
Title: Vectorized random generation of survival times
Version: 0.0.0.9999
Authors@R: c(
    person("Devin", "Incerti", , "devin.incerti@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Randomly draw survival times from survival curves without making 
    parametric assumptions in an efficient manner. Code is written in C++ so 
    that each individual can have a unique survival function. 
